dsDescriptionValue.value:
(rev. 2020-08-01)
Request dataset here: https://champshealth.org/data-access/

Version 4.1 of the standard, de-identified CHAMPS dataset included these files: case demographics (including MITS measurements), verbal autopsy, DeCoDe results, TAC results, and lab results. One new column (site_iso_code) was added to this dataset to the file CHAMPS_deid_basic_demographics.csv. This dataset is updated monthly. The version of this dataset changes quarterly when a revised ICD-10 mapping document is uploaded.
